@NODE "Opis"

	DBMS  is  pack  of  Arexx's scripts which can be used to manage bigger
  data bases,  generated  by  DB  by David Eckholm.  That scripts will do many 
  boring things instead you.

	I didn't  made it thinking about every data bases that can be made for 
  DB. This is for database, that I'm using to store information about many
  programs. 

	This pack contains:

	@{"DB_CopyContents" LINK CopyContentsDB}   - copies contents of previous record to next, but it
			     will be made only for selected fields.

	@{"DB_KonsolidujBazë" LINK KonsolidujBazëDB} - removes spces from names of programs, allow to save
			    some place on HD and simplify sorting.

	@{"DB_PokaûKategorie" LINK PokaûKategorieDB} - it's a little long, click to read details.

	@{"DB_ShowDataBase" LINK ShowDataBaseDB}  - exports  database,  but  only  records,  containing
			   infos about e.g.  newest programs  or  something you 
			   want.

        @{"DB_SzukajCiâgu" LINK SzukajCiâguDB}   - finds string in field 'Nazwa' and shows that, which
			    contains that string.

	@{"DB_SzukajAlternatywy" LINK SzukajAlternatywyDB} - finds  record  by  alternative  of  keys,   not
			       coniunction.

        @{"DB_OpusDB" LINK DB&OpusDB}            - select filename in Opus and order DB to find it
			       in database!

	@{"DB_Copy" LINK DBCopy}             - kopies record from one to another database.

	@{"DB_WyczyôêPola" LINK DBWyczyôêPola}      - clears all or selected fields in actual record.

	@{"DB_VisualInfo" LINK VisualInfo}	    - allow you to include gfx in database e.g. photos.
     
	@{"DB_CopyFilename2Realname.rexx" LINK CopyFilename} - copies data from one field, containing
					 datas about names of programs, to another.

@ENDNODE

