@NODE "PlanyNaPrzyszîoôê"

	- make scripts faster. It means - rewrite them in asm.

	- searching any fields for string.

	- show pic as soon as you go to record.

	- DB with DBM  is  slow.  I plan  to  make  my  own database with this
